title: New Leaf Elementals
description: A 100% vegan specialty coffee and tea shop serving chocolate and vanilla cupcakes, cookies and a range of coffee and tea. Also is a gift shop with crystals, salt lamps, vegan chocolate bars, stones, quartz, incense, music CDs, shawls, yoga mats An entire room with sofas and coffee tables for lounging while enjoying your cappuccino and cupcakes or cookies. Relaxing music is piped in and it is a great place to chill out and relax. Free wi-fi.
